  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个IPv4头部的包格式图，用于教学文档。这个头部是32位对齐的，我想用packet-beta语法来展示每个字段的位宽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "IPv4 Header Format"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，IPv4头部。我需要确认一下：这个图要不要显示具体的位编号？比如0-3这种起始和结束位置？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBits"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "要的，显示位编号很重要，这样学生能清楚每个字段占多少位。请在config里把showBits打开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "config",
        "showBits"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，配置已设置。现在开始画第一个字段：Version字段，4位，位0到3。这是IP协议的版本号，IPv4就是4。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Version (4)",
        "0-3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是IHL，Internet Header Length，也是4位，位4到7。这个字段表示头部的长度，以32位字为单位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IHL (4)",
        "4-7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "IHL已添加。下一个是Type of Service，8位，位8到15。这个字段现在叫DSCP和ECN，但传统上还是叫TOS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type of Service (8)",
        "8-15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，保持Type of Service这个名字，学生教材里还是这么叫的。接下来是Total Length，16位，位16到31。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Total Length (16)",
        "16-31"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Total Length已添加，覆盖位16-31。现在第一行32位满了。第二行开始是Identification，16位，位32到47，用于分片重组。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Identification (16)",
        "32-47"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Identification后面紧跟着Flags，3位，位48到50。然后是Fragment Offset，13位，位51到63。这两个字段都和分片有关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Flags (3)",
        "48-50",
        "Fragment Offset (13)",
        "51-63"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Flags和Fragment Offset都已添加，正好凑满第二行的32位。第三行开始是Time to Live，8位，位64到71。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Time to Live (8)",
        "64-71"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "TTL后面是Protocol字段，8位，位72到79，表示上层协议类型，比如TCP是6，UDP是17。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Protocol (8)",
        "72-79"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Protocol已添加。接下来是Header Checksum，16位，位80到95，用于校验头部完整性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Header Checksum (16)",
        "80-95"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Header Checksum。然后第四行是两个地址字段：Source Address 32位，位96到127；Destination Address也是32位，位128到159。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Address (32)",
        "96-127",
        "Destination Address (32)",
        "128-159"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个地址字段都已添加。现在到第五行了，接下来是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Address",
        "Destination Address"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第五行是Options字段，长度是可变的，从位160开始。然后是Padding，也是用来填充的，确保头部是32位对齐。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options (variable)",
        "160-191",
        "Padding",
        "192-223"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Options标注为variable，那它的结束位置怎么定？还有Padding的位范围？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Padding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Options通常画到位160-191，表示一个32位字的示例。Padding接着从192到223。这样整个头部最小20字节，最大60字节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options (variable)",
        "160-191",
        "Padding",
        "192-223"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Options和Padding都已添加。图基本完成了，我检查一下位编号有没有对齐。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Padding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我看一下。Identification是16位，位32-47，然后Flags是3位48-50，Fragment Offset是13位51-63。32+16+3+13=64，没错，第二行结束在63是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Identification",
        "Flags",
        "Fragment Offset"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我核对一下第三行：TTL 8位+Protocol 8位+Checksum 16位=32位，64-71, 72-79, 80-95，加起来正好到95，第四行从96开始，正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Time to Live",
        "Protocol",
        "Header Checksum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "标题也确认一下，用\"IPv4 Header Format\"，放在title里。这个图是给网络协议课程用的，要清晰易懂。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "IPv4 Header Format"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标题已设置。我再整体看一下：Version和IHL都是4位，但名字里括号标注了位宽，这样很清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Version (4)",
        "IHL (4)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个细节，Type of Service标注为8位，位8-15，这个没问题。但有些地方会写成DSCP(6位)+ECN(2位)，我们保持TOS 8位整体标注可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type of Service (8)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，保持Type of Service (8)的标注方式，更符合传统教材。整个图结构已经完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type of Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认一下Options和Padding的标注。Options是variable，表示长度可变；Padding没有标注位宽，因为它也是根据Options长度变化的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options (variable)",
        "Padding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Padding不标注位宽，只写\"Padding\"。Options标注为\"Options (variable)\"。这样处理很准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Padding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对了，Header Checksum确认一下名字，是\"Header Checksum\"还是\"Checksum\"？RFC里是Header Checksum。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Header Checksum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我检查了一下，当前写的是\"Header Checksum (16)\"，位80-95，是正确的。没有需要修改的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Header Checksum (16)"
      ],
